- # Shown when an assignment_view launch can't be matched to any known line
- # item — e.g. a manually created Canvas assignment, or a column whose mapping
- # isn't captured yet. Styled like the other in-iframe landings so it doesn't
- # read as a broken page; the explanation is the whole message (there's no
- # Dashboard content to drill into for an unmatched assignment).
.lti-iframe__landing
  = image_tag '/assets/images/wiki-logo.png', alt: 'Wiki Education Dashboard', class: 'lti-iframe__logo'
  %p.lti-iframe__title= t('lti.assignment_view.orphan.explanation')
